Package: eva
Architecture: amd64
Version: 0.3.12-1
Maintainer: Andreas Mueller <amu@gnoppix.com>
Description: Eva P2P Messenger Client - Post-quantum encrypted messaging
 Eva is a decentralized messaging system using ML-KEM-1024 post-quantum
 encryption (US government standard). No phone number or email required.
 .
 Features:
  - ML-KEM-1024 + Double Ratchet end-to-end encryption
  - 3 bootstrap servers for redundancy (US/EU/Asia)
  - Optional relay for offline message delivery
  - Tor support for anonymity
  - Reflector Bot integration for latency testing
Depends: libssl3, libsqlite3-0
Section: net
Priority: optional